1) Start up a CouchDB 1.1 instance 

2) Install Kanso (requires node) dev branch:

    git clone git://github.com/caolan/kanso.git 
    cd kanso 
    git checkout -b dev origin/dev 
    git submodule init 
    git submodule update 
    bin/kanso -v
    0.0.7

3) Unzip pages package.

4) Push the pages and admin apps to your couch:

    kanso push pages
    kanso pushadmin pages

5) Create pages with the built-in Kanso admin and make your site.
